Build docker Image: docker build -t api -f location .
RUN: docker run -d -p 9000:9000 api
List all containers: docker ps 
List all (including stopped): docker ps -a 
docker stop container_id
docker rm container_id
docker rmi image_id
docker exec -it container_id COMMAND
docker exec -it container_id ls
docker exec -it container_id bash
docker logs container_id



Terraform
terraform init (to start terraform plugin, to download and to initialize)
terraform fmt (to format the code)
terraform validate
terraform plan
terraform apply
terraform workspace new <NAME> (for ex dev)
terraform workspace select dev
terrafrom workspace list
terraform workspace delete